title: Presidents Cup Capsules
text:
> Top News Presidents Cup Capsules United States' Bubba Watson, left, and teammate J.B. Holmes celebrate after defeating International team player's Adam Scott of Australia and Hedeki Matsuyama of Japan 3 & 2 in their foursome match at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015.(AP Photo/Ahn Young-joon) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
